text: "Chocolate Cake" is a 1991 song by rock band Crowded House. It is from their third studio album Woodface. It went to number 7 in New Zealand, number 9 in Canada, number 20 in Australia, number 27 in the Netherlands, number 34 in Belgium and number 69 in the United Kingdom.
